<msbt attribsize="8">
	<message label="001" attrib="00 00 00 27 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Hello" target="actor" targetSpec="" />到了釣魚大會這天，<delay20 />
<anim id="HappyDance" target="actor" targetSpec="" />從早上開始就覺得好緊張喔～！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="002" attrib="00 00 00 27 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Love" target="actor" targetSpec="" />如果覺得釣到的魚<delay8 />和自己很有緣，<delay20 />
<anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />就這樣直接帶回家養也不錯唷～<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="003" attrib="00 00 00 27 00 00 00 00"><anim id="HappyDance" target="actor" targetSpec="" />今天我要盡情享受<delay8 />
這次的釣魚大會～！<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Thinking" target="actor" targetSpec="" />可是如果一隻都釣不到的話該怎麼辦啊～<pageBreak /><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />是說<delay8 />我每次像這樣
快要放棄的時候，<delay20 />
<anim id="Greeting" target="actor" targetSpec="" />都會突然釣到魚唷！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="004" attrib="00 00 00 26 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />雖然大家都說釣魚的關鍵在時機，<delay20 />
<anim id="Thinking" target="actor" targetSpec="" />但我覺得要釣到魚，<delay8 />
<anim id="Greeting" target="actor" targetSpec="" />好運也是必要的唷！<pageBreak /><anim id="Hesitate" target="actor" targetSpec="" />所以啊，<delay20 />我每天早上
都會先確認當天的星座運勢，<delay8 />
<anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />然後才出門釣魚喔～<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="005" attrib="00 00 00 26 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Greeting" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你想參加釣魚大會的話，<delay20 />
好像只要跟在廣場的<colour id="3" />俞司廷<colour id="65535" />說一聲，<delay20 />
<anim id="QuestionMark" target="actor" targetSpec="" />就可以了吧？<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
</msbt>